To: 玉山銀行
E.SUN BANK
收件單位:

DOCUMENTARY CREDIT

(若非本行通匯行則由銀行指定)|TEL:
【20】 CREDIT NO.信用狀號碼
(由銀行填寫)

AIRMAIL BRIEF CABLE

【32B】AMOUNT NOT EXCEEDING 金額 (小寫)
|SAY(大寫)
【42】AVAILABLE BY DRAFTS AT
□SIGHT【即期L/C,不申請 貴行融資】
□SIGHT (INTEREST FOR BUYER'S ACCOUNT, TENOR DAYS AFTER SIGHT) 【買方遠期 L/C】
USANCE_ DAYS AFTER SIGHT/AFTER B/L DATE/
承兌費 ACCEPTANCE CHARGE ARE FOR BENEFICIARY'S
【43P】PARTIAL SHIPMENTS 分批裝運
(如未註明者,概以「准許」開發)
申請日期:
【31】 DATE OF ISSUE 開狀日期
FCA FOB CFR CIF CIP EX-WORKS CPT LOCAL DELIVERY IN
跨頁請蓋騎縫章(原留印鑑)
單 位
匯率
營利事業統一編號:
【39】L/C AMOUNT TOLERANCE: + _%/-_____%
【45】DESCRIPTION OF GOODS:貨物內容 (請概括綜列,勿太冗長,但仍需儘可能加註貨品之數量及單價)
CABLE
(INTEREST FOR SELLER'S ACCOUNT) 【賣方遠期 L/C】
APPLICANT'S ACCOUNT(如未註明,視為受益人負擔)
【43T】TRANSHIPMENT 轉運
(如未註明者,概以「不准許」開發)
ALLOWED NOT ALLOWED
ALLOWED NOT ALLOWED
【44A】PLACE OF RECEIPT 【44E】PORT OF LOADING/AIRPORT【44F】 PORT OF DISCHARGE/AIRPORT
(請註明國別)
OF DEPARTURE(請註明國別)
OF DESTINATION(請註明國別)
裝載港:

收貨地:
經辦
|EXPIRY PLACE 信用狀有效地點
IN THE BENEFICIARY'S COUNTRY
□OTHERS:
年月
【44C】LATEST DATE OF SHIPMENT 最後裝運日
【44B】PLACE OF FINAL
DESTINATION/PLACE OF
DELIVERY (請註明國別)

『本申請書為一式多張,請加蓋騎縫章』
